==English==

===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*dʰeh₁-}}
Either borrowed from {{bor|en|frm|abscondre}} or directly from {{bor|en|la|abscondō||hide}}; formed from {{m|la|abs}}, {{m|la|ab||away}} + {{m|la|condō||put together, store}}, from {{m|la|con-||together}} + {{m|ine-pro|*dʰeh₁-||to put, place, set}}.<ref>{{R:CDOE|page=4}}</ref>
* Cognate with {{m|en|sconce||a type of light fixture}}.

